_Beyond\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Journey_Beyond\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Now that Journey Beyond has returned to being a free-standing company, we are looking at future growth and expansion,\\\" Journey Beyond CEO, Chris Tallent, said.\", \"from\": 1547, \"to\": 1707, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1557, \"end\": 1571, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Journey_Beyond\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Journey Beyond\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Journey_Beyond\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Journey_Beyond\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We know that a Journey Beyond experience delivers special and unique access, an authentic and more immersive experience and extraordinary service, and we want Australia to know that too.\", \"from\": 1709, \"to\": 1896, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1869, \"end\": 1878, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9999998396724679, \"rank\": 1.5372820012959898e-07, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are proud to be building that association with Journey Beyond.\\\"\", \"from\": 1897, \"to\": 1963, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1947, \"end\": 1961, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Journey_Beyond\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Journey Beyond\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Journey_Beyond\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Journey_Beyond\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Special offers will run alongside the campaign on hero products, further incentivising Australian travel.\", \"from\": 1965, \"to\": 2070, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Ghan is an Australian icon - and rightly so.\", \"from\": 2071, \"to\": 2119, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2071, \"end\": 2079, \"titl